Fully rented at $1,250 per apartment ($5,000 per month), tenants pay their own utilities (separated) and all have kitchens, formal dining rooms, 2 bedrooms and their own private front balcony/deck. 10% + cap rate. 1 year old roof! Updates in all units, hardwood floors, some newer kitchen cabinets, stainless appliances, tiled kitchens & backsplash, updated tiled baths, some granite countertops in kitchen.  Apartments are rented on Month-to-month basis.  One tenant enjoys off street parking.
